{"title":"我要他粮食堆成山","authors":["张明权"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":4,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要他粮食堆成山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗外头鸡叫三更天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我梦见粮食堆成山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"槽头上驴叫四更天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我急忙起来把衣穿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大小子才娶了新媳妇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闩着屋门睡得甜；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二小子今年才十四，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喊上几遍听不见。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全家大小都喊起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收拾好犁耙套老犍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出村来风吹精神爽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到地里黑土软绵绵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少人早已下了地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个比一个干得欢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清早做到东南晌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上午做到太阳偏西南。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看那犁铧、耧脚、锄面、铁锨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一晃一晃像打闪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你听那“得得”“??”“唷唷”“咧咧”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东地西地到处喊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身上的汗浸湿了袄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸上的汗滴脚前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做到太阳落下去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做到星星出满天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老婆喊我回家吃晚饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我说，“乘着好月亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这块地今夜收拾完。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老婆说我年轻了三十岁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我说，“今天不干等那天？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这地是咱们的地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这天是咱们的天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们还惜什么力和汗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"单等今年秋天到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干出来一个好丰年！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大囤流来小囤尖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缸里柜里都盛满；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看那"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小麦、大麦、谷子、豆子、高粱、玉米、棉花、红薯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一堆一堆堆成山！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四月七日，平原。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}